1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,200
Get transcript from YouTube video.

2
00:00:02,200 --> 00:00:05,100
First, open the YouTube app on your device,

3
00:00:05,100 --> 00:00:08,200
and tap on the video for which you want to get the transcript.

4
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:11,500
Now at the description, tap on more.

5
00:00:11,500 --> 00:00:14,000
Here, click on the show transcript.

6
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:16,500
You can see the transcript, and that's it.

